type: software
title: "Agent World Compiler PoC"
abstract: >
  A minimal proof-of-concept for a conference talk about securing agentic AI
  by converting observed agent execution traces into least-privilege runtime
  boundaries (World Manifests) and enforcing deterministic allow/deny decisions.
